      "comment": "MANIFESTO (2) hit the ground running last time with a strong early split and tried to lead throughout but had to settle for the minors when second (30.82) at this track over 530m. Can measure up this time. ATTENTION SEEKER (4) stalked the lead from the inside draw before finishing third last start (19.93) at this track in Best 8 over 342m. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expected to be in the finish again. HI THERE FRANK (1) failed to feature last start after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won by a nose at this track (30.84) beating Victory Club in a Invitation on February 19. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. BINNAWAY SANDS (6) looks an each-way chance.",
